        "created_at": "2021-07-19T13:55:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>They also did very well in 2019. \u201819s are a touch more concentrated and a touch more tightly wound out of the gates, but with a few years\u2019 bottle age I suspect they will hit even higher highs.</p>\n<p>Perri\u00e8re is one of the younger vine bottlings, if you want to see just how good they can get, try the Sous le Ch\u00e2teau and Sous la Velle bottlings.</p>",
