        "created_at": "2021-07-19T14:08:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"172148\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>\u2026and, if you want to enjoy the view over Sous la Velle, here it is: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/@46.9999222,4.7138115,3a,75y,116.99h,95.52t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sq__C51dklc4Aq_TZFTzGkQ!2e0!7i16384!8i8192\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Google Maps</a></p>\n<p>One of the most beautiful places in Burgundy!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Positively bucolic!</p>\n<p>I actually also have one bottle of Sous la Velle from the same vintage - as per your note, I think I\u2019ll likely hold off for another year or two before opening.</p>",
